reviews:
Easy to tighten and adjust.
The desk clamp mount hasn't budged once since installed months ago.
All nessicary hardware included with good instructions.
Honestly, a great mount all around.
Its 100 meduim quality darts, for the money worth the odd dart being messed up. Nothing disappointing, nothing special.

Have used this set a number of times now with no complaints, they feel comfortable to hold and use.
Even more important, don't tug or slip when cutting.
Some of the accessories are clearly value adds, but both scissors are fantastic quality, razor sharp and easy to clean.

Lets start with the general top complaint;

I've never had the issues with pressure or fit others have seem to have, the band is adjustable to a certain degree and cheap to replace if worn out.

The sound in game is fantastic, although coming off of some more studio focused headphones the music experience is less then desirable out of the box.

Thankfully, the software allows for in depth control and allows for multiple profiles to tune each of your experiences.

The mic isn't out of this world, but no worse then competitors in this price range so no complaints on that regard.

Battery life is fantastic, a small issue is the audible beep every 20 seconds or so if the battery is low.

I highly reccomend if most of what you do is gaming.

review_title: Never using anything again but ratchet!
reviews:
The mechanism takes a couple days to get used to, but once you have it down it's the best way to keep your pants up out there.
Ratchet is in small enough increments to get the perfect fit and style is very subtle and clean.

These are great! I’ve only had them for a week but so far I’m loving them, they fit nicely and don’t feel like they are going to fall out, they sound great, and also the distance that you can walk away from whatever is playing your music is great! I have recommended these to a co worker as we work rotating closing shifts and it’s great to be able to listen to music while closing and not have to worry about headphone cords

Works great and I love the product, but after purchasing and realizing I love it , I reached out to my regular hair dresser and asked if she could get it for me... turns out she even has it in stock and it’s $20 for 6fl oz where as this one is $15 for 2fl oz so it’s cheaper to get it from her !

review_title: Everything is sharp, not just the knife.
reviews: If you like razor sharp stamped steel utensils these are for you. Even the spoon is so sharp you can cut your meat. Sarcasm aside, the quality is very poor, the metal is oxidized and because of the stamping process it's left the edges super sharp. The manufacturer has clearly cut costs at one of the most basic steps of making a utensil set (rolling the stamped parts around in a tub of ceramic or steel beads) which only helps solidify their negligence and disregard for the quality of their products. Just think of running a razor out of the left and right side of your mouth before buying this item.

LOVEEEE THIS PRODUCT! I always tell people about this amazing product it’s so good smelling and makes your hair so soft in just a few minutes , and you don’t need a lot of it at once (just a dime size) and my hair is long and wavy. Great price for the size of the bottle too

review_title: Quality soap, suds nice and smells great.
reviews: This soap always blows me away with the cleaning power and shine. Only compaint is that the bottle becomes a little hard to handle without a handle.

The seal was excellent, the price was good but the quality was lacking. An oversight in the design leads to the flip top resting on your nose when in use. Simple fix would be to have an option to clip it, but that is not present
Had a stuck button on my controller. This kit included everything I needed to disassemble, fix and reassemble an Xbox One controller. No scratches or broken clips in sight
Fit on pillows is slightly big. Loose threads are a slight problem. They are smooth and very comfortable otherwise.
I'm 5'2", I have short legs and a tall desk. Allows for comfortable working.

It's light so easy to throw out and it's also very absorbent and odor reducing. The clumps it forms are solid and rarely get stuck to the sides of the box. Easy to scoop and pour, everything about this litter is convenient for both me and my cats

review_title: Quality of gun and foam is outstanding.
reviews: Everything this gun is feels premium. The construction is rigid plastics and metals. The dials are easy to read and are useful. The thing eats through car soap but with a bit of practice you can get fast and precise enough to get a whole car done with 4oz of soap. Highly recommended as long as you have at least the recommend water pressure and no less.

I'm not going to say that these are premium shelves by any stretch but the ease of installation and the sheer feel of them could convince me. They come with all the hardware you need and have a completely screw and nail free floating look. I wouldn't put much weight on them, maybe a couple books, but they hold little items off my desk and looks stunning above it.

review_title: Very wide brush, good quality though
reviews: It has an excellent hand feel, the handle is a non slip rubber that stays non slip even when covered in soap and water. The only problem I've experienced with this brush is that it is to wide to squeeze in between my rim spokes. The gap is about 3/4 inch and it can almost do it but not really. If you have more space in between you rim spokes it's highly recommended.

review_title: Good brush set, use all the time
reviews: Brushes are soft and fitted very well to the handles. They have a slight non slip paint or something on the handles as well so they won't be slippery when wet. They are easy to maintain and the case, although cardboard, is robust enough to store them in if dry.

review_title: Heavy and odor lock is poor.
reviews: It's heavy, which on its own is already a down side but when combined with the fact that it also makes the air stale and the odor locking last for less then 8 hours, it means you come home to a nasty smelling house after work every day.

review_title: Gold standard of tire and rim cleaning
reviews: I've tried many other products to help clean off the brownish residue that has built up over my tires, not one of them did what this can do. A good soak with the product, quick scrub with a tire brush and all old tire shine and brake dust will come off perfect with a spray of water.

review_title: They're nice quality and the grind is easily adjustable to any ...
reviews: They're nice quality and the grind is easily adjustable to any size. Only problem is that the caps have lips on the inside that catch whatever you grind, can cause too much to come out if you don't pay attention. This problem is easily solvable by giving the grinder a few shakes after usage.

review_title: had to use the full bottle (1/2 bottle per use as the directions say) but it made it drain like new.
reviews: It worked miracles on my clogged shower drain, had to use the full bottle (1/2 bottle per use as the directions say) but it made it drain like new.
It's pepper for a reputable company, what else is there to say.

review_title: Excellent pair of boots at this price
reviews:
Excellent pair of boots at this price, they aren't too heavy so they're easy to keep on all day.
Good traction in mud and ice grippers fit great because of the ledge on the heel.
No leaks after multiple months of nails and lumber so only good things to say.
All together a great boot.

review_title: I am happy with this purchase
reviews:
I purchased this vacuum for the sole purpose of using it for my car. I am happy with this purchase.
The vacuum is strong enough to pull up dirt that is deep into floor mats, and makes short work of seat seams and tight spots when using the brush attachments.
A bonus is that the blower when used with the narrowing attachment makes an excellent touchless car dryer, surprisingly powerful.

review_title: Old fashioned material but nice all around great product
reviews: The material is a little weird and cheap looking but the colour is beautiful and the fit is nice, I would buy again even though the material is not what I expected

review_title: Great if you want to punch 4 massive holes in ...
reviews: There should have been some double sided tape included in the kit as well. Great if you want to punch 4 massive holes in the wall, but even better when you need to move your desk and now your headphone stand is on the other side of the room. Quality is excellent so if you are okay with punching holes and know you are never going to move your desk the I would recommend.

review_title: At first I was very disappointed at how thin the material was
reviews: At first I was very disappointed at how thin the material was, but as I gave it chance when I took a trip I was very impressed. The material is so light it cuts pounds off of a travel bag, and when you are carrying it around all day this is a welcome change. Zippers all feel premium and accent the bag nicely and the handles are secured to the bag very well. My only concern to anyone else is that the bag has no "give" when the bag is full, you can try to force zipper close but the material the bag is made of does not stretch so you risk splitting the zipper or stitches.

review_title: Noticed certain cables such as laptop chargers and some micro usb chargers are to thick to fit easily, require a little bit of attention to get ...
reviews: The material is a a dense rubber with a soft touch rubber exterior. Does it's job and cables almost click into place. Noticed certain cables such as laptop chargers and some micro usb chargers are to thick to fit easily, require a little bit of attention to get into place.

reviews: Very good quality for the price, but if you are looking for easy obsorbancy this cloth doesnt like to suck up water untill it has a little water in it already, mildly annoying when starting a car but works perfectly by the end.

review_title: Good addition to a wood shop
reviews: Standard, decent quality drill bits for constant use if drilling wood but very brief and light use if drilling anything harder, such as tin or thin steel plate. Good addition to a wood shop.
